 2 crew habs, spinning dumbell. Each one can house the entire crew in emergency, but allows for more comfort normally.<br>
Spin for partial G during cruise, build extra truss after the ship reaches the destination, for full G for fully shielded habs (the difference between ~60 ton, ~400 meter trusses during cruise, and ~7000 ton, ~1400 meter for the final base which the habs are built up to become.)<br>
